message.raw:
Split Connect Camera into two parts, one for the UI and the other for reading
the h5 file.

Created StartCamera.vi as the code to read the h5 file.

Added Bias_Client.vi and Bias_Wrapper.vi as a client/server set of VI's that
allows many copies of BIAS to run in a single imbedded window in the server.
